sp.p:
They are of one length, ſir, take your choice;
(preſenting the ſwords)
you have injured me in the tendereſt point, injured me in my love —knowing I was a citizen, you preſumed I would not reſent an affront from a ſoldier; but I will convince you, ſir, that in this country, a ſoldier and a citizen are one character.
